-- Reliance Industries Advances Helping India's Sensex Index Erase Losses
-- Margo Towie
-- 2010-06-30T04:06:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-30/reliance-industries-advances-helping-india-s-sensex-index-erase-losses.html

          
          
             India’s stocks pared losses, with
the benchmark Bombay Stock Exchange’s Sensitive Index little
changed at 17,530.41 as of 9:34 a.m. local time. The gauge had
earlier fallen as much as 0.9 percent. Reliance Industries Ltd.,
India’s most valuable company, gained 1.5 percent.  
          
          


  


        